# Track ONLY explicit configs and the commands library.
# Anything else Claude Code writes to ~/.claude (sessions, history, caches,
# transcripts, todos, telemetry, statsig, plugins, machine-local settings,
# new things added in future versions) is ignored by default.

# Default-deny
*

# Whitelist
!.gitignore
!settings.json
!commands/
!commands/**
!hooks/
!hooks/**
!skills/
!skills/**
